author: Erin Durkin
title: NYC death toll jumps by 3,700 after uncounted fatalities are added
description: The city now has more than 10,000 deaths.
content:
Seven car in New York City | AP Photo
New York Citys official coronavirus death toll has soared past 10,000, after thousands of deaths that previously went uncounted were added to the citys statistics.
